      {"view":"Risk automation is underrated.","question":"How does IBKR protect downside in stress periods?","answer":"Automated liquidation and collateral workflows reduce delay risk in volatile markets, helping preserve capital while supporting tighter pricing for customers."},
      {"view":"Growth is now multi-channel.","question":"Is this still just a retail trading story?","answer":"No. Introducing brokers, advisors, and institutional flows increasingly use IBKR infrastructure, expanding TAM without abandoning core retail economics."}
